CardData.FlavorText: …he noticed a place of dense black shadow ahead of him black even for that forest, like a patch of midnight that had never been cleared away. As he drew nearer, he saw that it was made by spider-webs one behind and over and tangled with another. —The Hobbit

Localization.Title: Spiders' Nest
Localization.Text: You destroy the Spiders' nest. Cannot engage while King Spider is in play
